frameDefinitions: An Agent intends and takes steps towards bringing about a State_of_affairs or, metonymically, towards acquiring a Sought_entity .
A Helper benefits a Benefited_party by enabling the culmination of a Goal that the Benefited_party has.
An Experiencer desires that an Event occur.
A Cognizer_agent attempts to find some Sought_entity by examining some Ground.
A Cognizer has a relatively fixed positive or negative point of view towards an Issue.
frameExamples: Will you <t>help</t> the Government find your brother?
I only <t>wanted</t> one piece of candy.
In interviews , it seems like everyone is completely <t>against</t> this expenditure .
listRoleDefinitions: The <fen>Agent</fen> makes an attempt to achieve a <fen>State_of_affairs</fen> or to  obtain a <fen>Sought_entity</fen>.
The entity that the <fen>Agent</fen> attempts to acquire.
A state or event that the <fen>Agent</fen> wants to bring about. The Agent may but need not be a participant in that <fen>State_of_affairs</fen>.
This role identifies the <fen>Time</fen> when the attempt occurs.
The place where the <fen>Agent</fen> is seeking to achieve a particular <fen>State_of_affairs</fen> or to acquire a <fen>Sought_entity</fen>.
The <fen>Benefited_party</fen> receives a benefit from the action of the <fen>Helper</fen>.
The <fen>Helper</fen> performs some action that benefits the <fen>Benefited_party</fen>.
The desirable state of affairs that the <fen>Benefited_party</fen> is involved in and which is enabled by the <fen>Helper</fen>.
This role identifies a <fen>Focal_entity</fen> involved in achieving the <fen>Goal</fen>.
This role identifies the <fen>Time</fen> when the Assistance occurs.
This role identifies the <fen>Place</fen> where the Assistance occurs.
The <fen>Experiencer</fen> is the person (or sentient being) who wishes for the <fen>Event</fen> to occur.
The change that the <fen>Experiencer</fen> would like to see.
This is the entity that the <fen>Experiencer</fen> wishes to be affected by some <fen>Event</fen>.
The <fen>Location_of_event</fen> is the place involved in the desired <fen>Event</fen>.
The <fen>Time</fen> is when the <fen>Experiencer</fen> desires something.
Where the event takes place.  Note that this role is of extremely rare occurrence in this frame.
The person who attempts to find the Sought_entity.
This is the entity that the <fen>Ground</fen> may contain. Typically, it is expressed as a <ment>for</ment>-PP.
This role identifies the <fen>Time</fen> when the Seeking occurs.
A spatial setting larger than the <fen>Ground</fen> in which the Seeking event occurs.
The individual that holds an opinion on an <fen>Issue</fen> or Side.
The matter, usually concerning a course of action, which the <fen>Cognizer</fen> has a positive or negative opinion about.
The party or individual (generally associated with a particular position on an <fen>Issue</fen>) that the <fen>Cognizer</fen> has an opinion about.
An action taken by a <fen>Side</fen> or a view that the <fen>Side</fen> takes on an issue which the <fen>Cognizer</fen> either supports or opposes.
The time period during which the <fen>Cognizer</fen> has the indicated point of view towards the <fen>Issue</fen>.
The location where the <fen>Cognizer</fen> takes <fen>Side</fen>s on an <fen>Issue</fen> .
listRoleExamples:
<fex>Those states</fex> sought a remedy that would substantially change the company's business
practices.
Or the monstrous Saddam, who filled mass graves to bursting, invaded two neighboring countries, and avidly sought <fex>weapons of mass destruction</fex>.
The disclosure came as prosecutors successfully sought <fex>in federal court</fex> to keep Luise Garofalo behind bars.
Whoever didn't cook has to help <fex>with the dishes</fex>.
The police assisted Harry in finding his cat <fex>on Wednesday afternoon</fex>.
The police assisted Harry in finding his cat <fex>in front of his house</fex>.
I want that box <fex>on top of the other one</fex>.
Oh, so <fex>now</fex> you want to go to the zoo!
<fex>In the car</fex> I had desired nothing more than to get here, but now that I'm here...
The police were hunting for evidence in my house <fex>yesterday</fex>
<fex>In Paris</fex> police were hunting for suspects in two of the city's southerns suburbs today
<fex>Last year</fex> she opposed the bill, but changed her mind after she received correspondence supporting the bill.
